manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: WHY CHOOSE OUR GEL SEAT CUSHION? NO HOT SEAT ANYMORE - This ventilated gel cushion has been designed to maintain proper temperature. With an air mesh cover that is breathable and washable it allows a maximum amount of air flow through the cushion. Forget about the heat and the irritation from previous experience. This cushion certainly will make a difference. RELIEF PAIN - It is difficult for people with back pain to sit with comfort. This cushion is designed to relieve the pain from lumbar, hip, tailbone and coccyx. The high quality gel hugs tailbone and maintains its shape and contour without compromising the comfort. Study shows people with back pain are able to sit longer period of time with this cushion than any other leading brand on the market today. MODIFIED CUSHION COVER - Newly designed cushion-cover has added a non-slip feature. The cover is also removable and washable. SIT WITH GREAT COMFORT - The design of our seat and lower back cushion will provide pressure relief on your tailbone and lower back area.The back support will make anything you sit on feel more comfortable.

Fantastic - You Can Sit on an Egg! Your achy spine and backside on our Gel Seat Cushion, the support cushion that supports so well that you can sit on an egg without breaking it. Say goodbye to sore, stiff muscles caused by sitting all day or long car rides. Standard support cushions need a hole cut out of the cushion to support your tailbone. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my Jeep seats and then I bought more for the beach, my 86 year old mom for her injury she sustained when she fell, and stadium seating. I put them in my shopping bag and easy to transport. Very cushioned and great price for the quality

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Use at home or restaurants etc
reviews.reviewText: My dad is 91 and has little personal "padding" when he sits. I purchased this for him to take out to restaurants with no padded seating. Since he uses a cane I found a canvas bag easier to carry the seat mat. Look at the photos, this is not memory foam but is comfortable and durable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable when sitting on a wooden chair for more than one hour.
reviews.reviewText: I like this seat cushion. It solves my problems when sitting in a wooden chair for more than one hour. It does however, move around on the chair, and will even work itself off the chair. I just have to replace it on the chair, and am ready to work again. I am very pleased with this egg-shell cushion. I do use the included the pad cover, which may encourage it to move around. I am more pleased to have this cushion, than to continue to sit on my very hard wooden chair.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The texture of the gel is uncomfortable, and it is oddly firm which actually increases pain to sit on. It definitely does not work as a seat cushion if you have pressure pain when sitting. I’m trying it as a back cushion now instead. Not sure about that either, but it is at least not immediate discomfort like it is for sitting.

My physical therapist recommended these to me. I have lumbar problems and was in a lot of pain.I have 3 gel seat cushions around the house, and sitting on hard surfaces (kitchen table chair) and in my computer chair are much more comfortable on my back. I can even get up and be able to walk without stiffness/limpimg or significant pain.These don't work as well on soft surfaces (sofa), but I am glad to have these -- they really help.

reviews.reviewTitle: Excellent, just as described and reviewed.
reviews.reviewText: This is a weird looking and weird feeling product but works excellent for long days sitting.

This seat cushion looks so comfortable in pictures, but in reality, it's not very comfortable. It was quite hard and the honeycomb design feels very weird to sit on. Sat on it for about 10 minutes and decided I had to return it.
Exactly as promised. Feel coolness as soon as you sit down and is maintained. Very comfortable.
